msgstr "སྒྲོམ་ལམ་གཞིར་བཟོ་བའི་གྲངས་ཀ་ཉུང་བ།"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/edit_jsp.java:905
msgid ""
"Reduce tunnel count when idle to conserve resources but keep tunnel open (to "
